sequenceDiagram
  participant U as User / Browser
  participant ASR as ASR layer
  participant API as VoiceForge API
  participant LLM as LLM triage
  participant TTS as TTS layer
  participant UI as Latency waterfall UI

  U->>ASR: Speech or text input
  ASR-->>API: transcript + asr_ms
  API->>LLM: triage request
  Note over LLM: Mock / Ollama / DomainForge /v1/query
  LLM-->>API: reply JSON + llm_ttft_ms
  API->>TTS: synthesize reply
  Note over TTS: edge-tts or browser speechSynthesis
  TTS-->>API: audio_b64 or use_browser_tts
  API-->>UI: result + latency budget breakdown
  API-->>U: audio or text fallback

  alt degradation
    API-->>U: text-only / cached reply / browser TTS
  end
